Greenpeace Planet3 Client Code Rewrite
---------------------------------------

Welcome to the planet3 client code rewrite code repository.
Our aim is to optimize the html/js/css code of the current 
greenpeace.org website.

Check out our wiki for more information:
https://github.com/stripthis/Greenpeace-CSS/wiki

---------------------------------------

Additional info
===================================

SASS
-------------------------------------------------------------
Please note that the CSS files are written in SASS

SASS is a Ruby based CSS precursor.
Its like LESS but without the fuss, mess & anguish.

the file format used is .scss

How to install Compass SASS
http://compass-style.org/install/

when you have it installed run:
$ cd Greenpeace-CSS (or path/to/project)
$ compass watch

You should see:
#  >>> Compass is watching for changes. Press Ctrl-C to Stop.

Feel free to skype me if you have any problems.

PHP
------------------------------------------------
This project uses PHP to stitch together the templates.
You will need a personal PHP development enviroment.

Mac OS-X 
http://www.mamp.info/en/index.html

Windows
http://www.apachefriends.org/en/xampp.html